In 2006 and 2007, a public committee fought against the [Diocese of Voronezh](/Diocese_of_Voronezh)'s attempts to claim ownership of the [Ryazan Kremlin](/Ryazan_Kremlin). A rather spirited defense of historical property, wouldn't you say?

